title: Linda Eder - And So Much More (1994)
description:
As I was browsing through Tower Records at the time in 1994 when this CD was released, I realized that I stumbled upon one of the best female vocalists I had ever heard...  this was worth every penny I paid for it.  If you are a lover of Barbra Streisand or Celine Dion, then you are in for a real treat.  

"And So Much More" is Linda Eder&#039;s third album, and in my opinion is her best.  She really pours out the vocals here.  

I strongly recommend this, and any other album she has ever made.  I was surprised not to find this torrent out there, but I have since changed that... 

Enjoy and reseed!
